# PR Policy: Minimal

Pull request title and a brief summary of what changed and why.

## Rules

- Clear title describing the change
- One to three sentences summarising the purpose of the PR
- No required section structure

## Rationale

Suitable for small changes, solo projects, or teams where PR descriptions
are a formality rather than a primary review communication tool.
